Creating bins:

Income: 0-35000 - Low

Income: >35000-70000 - Medium

Income: >70000 - High

In [17]:
df['Income_level']=df.Income.apply(lambda x : 'Low' if x < 35000 else "Medium" 
                                   if (x >= 35000 and x < 70000) else "High")
In [18]:
cnt=sns.countplot(df.Income_level,palette="dark:#5A9_r")
plt.title('Count of customers')
for i in cnt.containers:
    cnt.bar_label(i)
plt.show()

Insight:

Most of the customers belong to medium Income level i.e. Income between 35000-70000

Conclusion¶

  1. Most of the customers belong to medium Income level i.e. Income between 35000-70000.

  2. Customers with no child have higher average income.

  3. People who earn more are likely to spend more.

  4. People with high income level purchase Liquor and meat products more than any other income level.

  5. 50% customers have education level Graduation.

  6. Basic education level stands out at low income level.

  7. The low level of education is reflected in the income level.

  8. Customer satistfaction is very high only 0.95% complains.

  9. Complainers have slightly lower income level.

  10. Most of the customers are married.

  11. Average income in all marital status are close.

  12. In all income levels we have almost same ratio of people belonging to different marital statuses.

  13. 50% of total spend by customers are spent on Wines category which is highest and second highest is meat category with 27% of total spend by customers.

  14. Sweets and Fruits category has lowest percentage in total spend by customers about 4% each.

  15. Medium level income customers like to purchase when discounts are there.

  16. Catalog purchases are almost equally done by high and medium income level customers.

  17. Maximum web and store purchases are done by Medium income level customers.

  18. Married customers are also more likely to purchase from web and stores.

  19. Campaign 2 was worst campaign only 1.35% of customers accepted it.

  20. Last campaign i.e. campaign 6 is most sucessful campaign 15.03% customers accepted it and customers from all income level showed interest in it.
